1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available.]

2
00:01:50,780 --> 00:01:55,500
[Crossroad Bistro]

3
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,440
I'm packing up

4
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:09,080
Xiaoyu's things.

5
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:09,960
You can't do that

6
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:11,440
without my permission.

7
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:13,840
If you dare get close to her,

8
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:15,640
believe it or not,

9
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:17,400
I'll risk my life to kill you.

10
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,920
Do remember.

11
00:02:18,920 --> 00:02:19,840
Don't tell Shanshan

12
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:21,480
about the fine.

13
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:22,440
And don't tell Feng Xi

14
00:02:22,440 --> 00:02:23,840
about what happened to Xiaoyu.

15
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:24,680
Sure.

16
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,720
I'll keep them in my mind.

17
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:27,840
I'll teach you two more dishes tonight.

18
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:28,600
Great.

19
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:29,600
I can learn more from you.

20
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:37,840
I miss you so much.

21
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,280
You had ten years to grasp the opportunity.

22
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:41,079
You gave it up within five minutes.

23
00:02:41,079 --> 00:02:41,920
I wasn't afraid of him.

24
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:43,240
I was afraid you two would be embarrassed.

25
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:44,200
Only the runaway would be embarrassed.

26
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:44,960
I'm going to see her now.

27
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:47,880
Boys should take the initiative.

28
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,000
If you like her,

29
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,120
go for her.

30
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:52,280
You're just fanning the flames.

31
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,600
They're young and impulsive.

32
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:54,840
What if they get in a fight?

33
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:56,280
Open the door.

34
00:03:01,820 --> 00:03:04,820
[Ep 24]

35
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,240
All right.

36
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,760
I will calm down.

37
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,760
I'm quite calm.

38
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:11,800
Feng Xi.

39
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:14,680
You're so wrong about me.

40
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,320
Think about it.

41
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,920
No matter whom you'll marry,

42
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:20,480
will you have to take the responsibility of

43
00:03:20,480 --> 00:03:22,120
looking after both sets of parents?

44
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:24,200
Li Xiang.

45
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,160
Do you know

46
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:28,920
what your only virtue is?

47
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,880
It's honesty.

48
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,040
You're so honest

49
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:35,079
that you don't give a damn
about people's feelings.

50
00:03:35,079 --> 00:03:36,560
You're so honest

51
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,800
that you don't hide your selfishness.

52
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,360
But today,

53
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,760
I'm telling you explicitly

54
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:41,800
that I don't want to.

55
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:44,120
I'm not the kite you bought.

56
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,400
Our relationship can't be decided by you

57
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,800
like you control the kite line.

58
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,600
I've already had a boyfriend.

59
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:53,680
Things between us are great.

60
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,720
Continue to do your research.

61
00:03:58,440 --> 00:04:00,280
You're not in my world anymore.

62
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,400
Feng Xi.

63
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:05,480
Feng Xi.

64
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,720
Don't fool yourself.

65
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,000
I know

66
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,600
you still love me.

67
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,120
Do you really think

68
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:16,160
the chef loves you?

69
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:17,200
If he loves you,

70
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,600
will he walk away?

71
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:21,480
How could someone like him

72
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:23,560
be more reliable than me?

73
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,240
I'm better than him in every way.

74
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:26,440
Feng Xi.

75
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,440
Even if you don't think about me,

76
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:29,680
think about yourself.

77
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,920
It's none of your business.

78
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:36,480
Come on, Feng Xi.

79
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:39,320
I know you are punishing me

80
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:40,360
in this way.

81
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,680
I'm totally fine with it.

82
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:42,600
I'm pleading guilty.

83
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:45,200
As long as we can get back together,

84
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:46,600
in the future,

85
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,560
I'm all yours.

86
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,520
All right?

87
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:53,920
Open the door!

88
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,040
What do you want?

89
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:02,240
Could I have a word?

90
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,520
Here?

91
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:05,320
Yes.

92
00:05:05,320 --> 00:05:06,160
Right here.

93
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:09,000
Go ahead.

94
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,520
Feng Xi.

95
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:12,720
I like you.

96
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:15,960
I'm not joking.

97
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:17,160
If I don't speak it out,

98
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,360
I'm afraid I won't have a second chance.

99
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:19,560
I'll love you

100
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,560
for the rest of my life.

101
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:22,360
I'll take care of you.

102
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,000
Will you accept me?

103
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:27,000
Don't talk nonsense, okay?

104
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,600
You are overreaching yourself,

105
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:30,320
you know?

106
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:31,080
I'm talking to Feng Xi!

107
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:32,440
Who are you to yell at me?

108
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:34,720
I shouldn't have been nice to you

109
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:36,000
when we first met.

110
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,760
You're just a damned chef.

111
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:40,760
You can never give her the future

112
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,440
that I can give to her.

113
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:42,840
Out!

114
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:43,800
Shut up!

115
00:05:49,080 --> 00:05:50,560
Wait for me outside.

116
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:52,159
Wait for me.

117
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:53,200
Sure.

118
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:06,920
Come here.

119
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:09,440
Sit down.

120
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:15,560
You won't believe this shit, will you?

121
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:17,960
Li Xiang.

122
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:20,240
Do you know how desperately I wanted

123
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:22,840
to hear you say those words?

124
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,200
You're right.

125
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:26,000
He's only a chef.

126
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,360
But he is a man.

127
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,960
You've always been a boy.

128
00:06:31,280 --> 00:06:32,680
You're well-educated with a bright future.

129
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:33,760
But he is responsible.

130
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,600
It's harder to make you responsible

131
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:37,320
than to make him educated.

132
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:48,080
What are you doing?

133
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,640
I asked him to leave

134
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:02,200
because I'd like to save your face.

135
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,280
Leave now.

136
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:04,640
No, I won't.

137
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:06,840
You can't treat me like that.

138
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:08,360
You treated me like that first.

139
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,520
I don't care.

140
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,480
Right now,

141
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:15,880
I have nowhere to go.

142
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:21,920
That's

143
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,400
the person I know.

144
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:35,600
The last thing I can do

145
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:37,280
is to allow you to stay over tonight.

146
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:38,159
I'm leaving.

147
00:07:39,440 --> 00:07:40,520
Please leave my home

148
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:41,400
before I go back tomorrow morning.

149
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,200
Otherwise, I'll call the police.

150
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,159
Did you come to save me from it

151
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:55,800
or confess your love?

152
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:09,640
Feng Xi.

153
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:11,000
I was returning the favor.

154
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:13,240
Every word I said was
from the bottom of my heart.

155
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:18,200
If these things

156
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:19,440
didn't happen,

157
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:22,680
would you keep these words
to yourself forever?

158
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:25,880
I realize

159
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:27,520
you really need to be pushed.

160
00:08:28,520 --> 00:08:29,160
You started with

161
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:31,000
giving a long speech.

162
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:32,320
Have you ever thought about

163
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:34,679
what if I don't accept you?

164
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:37,000
How do you know
I haven't thought of it?

165
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:39,240
I have.

166
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,720
If I hadn't said these words,

167
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,640
I'd have been very contented

168
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:45,720
with just seeing you in the bistro.

169
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:48,240
If I said something you don't accept,

170
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,120
I'd resign tomorrow.

171
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:51,360
Resign?

172
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:53,080
How dare you?

173
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:54,520
Just imagine.

174
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:56,400
If you had rejected me

175
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:57,960
and I had to see you every day in the bistro,

176
00:08:58,640 --> 00:09:00,080
how would I carry out my work?

177
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:05,320
When did I reject you?

178
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:10,080
Do you mean

179
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,200
you said yes?

180
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,720
I was going to say yes,

181
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,960
but now I need to consider it more.

182
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:16,480
Wait.

183
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,720
Consider what?

184
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:18,960
What do you need to consider?

185
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:21,160
I don't want you to think

186
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:24,440
the reason why I accept you

187
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:25,800
is that I fear the bistro
can't go well without you.

188
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,800
Why would I resign

189
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:29,880
if I'm doing a good job?

190
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:35,760
Repeat

191
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:38,200
what you just said.

192
00:09:39,160 --> 00:09:39,180
What?

193
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:40,680
Say it.

194
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,240
Don't look at me like this.

195
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:47,160
Now my mind is a blank.

196
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:49,440
Take your time.

197
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,000
Think about it.

198
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,160
Feng Xi.

199
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:09,400
I don't know since when

200
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:12,360
I started to care about you.

201
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:14,760
When I saw you hustling

202
00:10:14,760 --> 00:10:16,480
around the bistro,

203
00:10:18,160 --> 00:10:19,000
I felt bad.

204
00:10:21,760 --> 00:10:23,160
When I saw your ex

205
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:24,960
badgering you,

206
00:10:26,640 --> 00:10:27,680
I felt bad.

207
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:30,200
I felt not only bad,

208
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:32,000
but heartbroken.

209
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,400
I think I am in love with you.

210
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:42,520
So I've decided that,

211
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,440
from now on,

212
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:47,880
you

213
00:10:49,040 --> 00:10:50,240
will be taken care of by me.

214
00:11:11,520 --> 00:11:12,360
Period.

215
00:11:14,920 --> 00:11:15,960
What's wrong?

216
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:17,280
I'm fine.

217
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:20,480
I'm fine.

218
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:24,880
So, will you say yes?

219
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:45,040
Don't worry.

220
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:49,200
I will take good care of you.

221
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:27,880
Feng Xi.

222
00:12:27,880 --> 00:12:28,840
What?

223
00:12:29,280 --> 00:12:30,920
Do you carry your ID card with you?

224
00:12:31,880 --> 00:12:32,920
Yes.

225
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:33,560
What's wrong?

226
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:34,440
Weren't you being kind

227
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:36,400
to let him stay over?

228
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,760
I'm worrying

229
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:38,880
you could be homeless.

230
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:43,000
I was going to stay in a hotel.

231
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:48,640
What about me?

232
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:54,160
Can't you go home?

233
00:12:55,560 --> 00:12:56,560
It's not home

234
00:12:56,560 --> 00:12:57,520
without you.

235
00:12:59,440 --> 00:13:00,760
Why didn't I find

236
00:13:00,760 --> 00:13:02,360
you are so glib?

237
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:05,080
I'm not glib.

238
00:13:05,560 --> 00:13:06,320
I am just

239
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:07,560
being spontaneous.

240
00:13:09,400 --> 00:13:10,160
All right.

241
00:13:10,160 --> 00:13:11,720
You can sleep with your dad tonight.

242
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:13,120
And I'll sleep with your mom.

243
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,200
No problem.

244
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:18,560
I'm okay with that.

245
00:13:18,560 --> 00:13:20,000
But I'm afraid my mom won't agree to it.

246
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:31,280
Feng Xi.

247
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,360
I don't blame you.

248
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:34,560
I don't have to think about it.

249
00:13:34,560 --> 00:13:35,360
This bad idea

250
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:36,720
must come from Henan.

251
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:38,720
You don't need to apologize to me.

252
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:40,680
Mom.

253
00:13:40,680 --> 00:13:42,200
Now you're relieved.

254
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:43,440
So, can I say

255
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:45,480
we didn't cheat you?

256
00:13:45,920 --> 00:13:47,640
It's not cheating.

257
00:13:47,640 --> 00:13:48,280
It's called,

258
00:13:48,280 --> 00:13:50,240
"Good things take time."

259
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:50,720
Yes.

260
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:56,120
It isn't a wasted trip.

261
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:57,440
We're relieved to see

262
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:58,560
you two are together.

263
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:03,120
If I'm right,

264
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:04,480
Henan and you

265
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:05,840
have been into each other

266
00:14:05,840 --> 00:14:07,120
for a while.

267
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:08,560
But

268
00:14:08,560 --> 00:14:11,000
none of you wants to say it out,

269
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:11,600
right?

270
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:12,720
Auntie.

271
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:14,040
You have sharp eyes.

272
00:14:14,040 --> 00:14:14,600
Yeah.

273
00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:16,600
I've been an ideaistic mentor all my life.

274
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:17,760
A glance will suffice...

275
00:14:17,760 --> 00:14:19,240
To see everything through!

276
00:14:24,680 --> 00:14:29,000
Although you just started to get serious,

277
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:32,040
every word I said still counts.

278
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:33,600
Feng Xi.

279
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:35,720
Talk to your parents

280
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:37,320
and ask for their opinions.

281
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:38,480
All right?

282
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:39,160
Okay.

283
00:14:39,640 --> 00:14:41,800
Then we shall meet together.

284
00:14:41,800 --> 00:14:42,600
Dad.

285
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:43,920
Here we go again.

286
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:47,760
Bad boy.

287
00:14:47,760 --> 00:14:48,880
You are a lucky dog.

288
00:15:04,680 --> 00:15:05,520
Is everyone asleep?

289
00:15:06,120 --> 00:15:06,760
Yes.

290
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:09,320
Will you finish soon?

291
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:12,920
Send.

292
00:15:12,920 --> 00:15:13,840
Yes.

293
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:17,000
Not yet.

294
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:18,520
I'm still awake.

295
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:20,680
Who is that? It's so late.

296
00:15:20,680 --> 00:15:21,560
You Shanshan.

297
