00:37:11,920 --> 00:37:13,240
They also need platforms.

882
00:37:13,240 --> 00:37:14,480
In fact, these young people

883
00:37:14,480 --> 00:37:16,080
are very talented.

884
00:37:16,080 --> 00:37:17,640
But I'm afraid there's no place
to develop their talents.

885
00:37:17,640 --> 00:37:18,560
So,

886
00:37:18,560 --> 00:37:20,120
I produced a show.

887
00:37:20,120 --> 00:37:20,960
I've already invited

888
00:37:20,960 --> 00:37:21,880
popular musicians

889
00:37:21,880 --> 00:37:23,560
to be mentors

890
00:37:23,560 --> 00:37:24,560
in this show.

891
00:37:24,560 --> 00:37:26,520
But one important position

892
00:37:26,520 --> 00:37:27,440
is still vacant.

893
00:37:27,440 --> 00:37:28,640
The music director.

894
00:37:32,360 --> 00:37:33,200
Are you trying to

