00:37:34,760 --> 00:37:35,560
Yes.

897
00:37:35,560 --> 00:37:36,920
Then talk to him.

898
00:37:37,280 --> 00:37:38,680
If this can work,

899
00:37:38,680 --> 00:37:40,280
why will I talk to you?

900
00:37:40,280 --> 00:37:40,920
You've tried?

901
00:37:40,920 --> 00:37:42,040
I've tried.

902
00:37:42,040 --> 00:37:43,640
But it didn't work at all.

903
00:37:43,640 --> 00:37:45,200
You know Mr. Hei.

904
00:37:45,200 --> 00:37:46,680
When I was talking to him,

905
00:37:46,680 --> 00:37:48,120
he looked at me with a smile on his face.

906
00:37:49,440 --> 00:37:51,560
Or he used his hand as an excuse.

907
00:37:52,080 --> 00:37:53,200
I said, "Bro,

908
00:37:53,200 --> 00:37:54,360
don't fool me.

909
00:37:54,360 --> 00:37:56,360
You have already recovered.

910
00:37:56,360 --> 00:37:57,960
And you're independent."

911
00:37:58,440 --> 00:37:59,160
Yes.

912
00:37:59,160 --> 00:38:01,120
I gave him the best offer.

913
00:38:01,120 --> 00:38:02,200
The best offer.

914
00:38:02,640 --> 00:38:03,800
But he still said no.

915
00:38:03,800 --> 00:38:04,520
He didn't want to come.

916
00:38:06,520 --> 00:38:08,600
He's always been like that.

917
00:38:08,600 --> 00:38:09,680
He won't do anything

918
00:38:09,680 --> 00:38:11,160
if he doesn't want to.

919
00:38:11,160 --> 00:38:12,200
He doesn't care about

920
00:38:12,200 --> 00:38:13,480
people's reputations and money.

921
00:38:13,480 --> 00:38:15,120
I know.

922
00:38:15,120 --> 00:38:16,880
But you also know his influence

923
00:38:17,200 --> 00:38:18,040
in the music industry.

924
00:38:18,040 --> 00:38:19,240
He is the big shot.

925
00:38:19,520 --> 00:38:21,720
I worry that if he doesn't come,

926
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:24,000
my show will be a failure.

927
00:38:25,600 --> 00:38:26,880
Please help me.

928
00:38:28,560 --> 00:38:30,840
I'm not sure if I could.

929
00:38:33,160 --> 00:38:34,160
Have a try, okay?

930
00:38:34,160 --> 00:38:35,320
Give it a try.

931
00:38:35,320 --> 00:38:36,320
I'm waiting for the good news.

932
00:38:36,640 --> 00:38:37,560
Wait.

933
00:38:37,560 --> 00:38:39,720
I can't promise to give you the good news.

934
00:38:39,720 --> 00:38:40,880
But I can guarantee

935
00:38:40,880 --> 00:38:42,240
I can get you some information.

936
00:38:42,240 --> 00:38:44,480
That will work.

937
00:38:44,480 --> 00:38:46,120
Try your best, Shanshan.

938
00:38:46,120 --> 00:38:47,480
Try your best.

939
00:38:48,880 --> 00:38:49,800
All right.

940
00:39:16,360 --> 00:39:17,000
Sir.

941
00:39:17,720 --> 00:39:18,480
Could I

942
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:19,720
bum a cigarette?

943
00:39:22,200 --> 00:39:22,920
Thanks.

944
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:41,880
Flying abroad?

945
00:39:41,880 --> 00:39:42,520
Yes.

946
00:39:43,120 --> 00:39:44,000
Where are you heading to?

947
00:39:44,920 --> 00:39:45,640
Munich.

948
00:39:46,080 --> 00:39:46,640
What about you?

949
00:39:47,640 --> 00:39:48,200
Oslo.

950
00:40:02,040 --> 00:40:04,040
See you.

